text: Jérôme Nury (born 25 August 1972) is a member of the National Assembly of France representing the third constituency of Orne. ==References== Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:People from Valence, Drôme Category:Politicians from Normandy Category:Deputies of the 15th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:The Republicans (France) politicians
